===================================================================

Python / Flask Standard .gitignore

===================================================================

1. Virtual Environment

Kabhi bhi virtual environment folder ko push nahi karna chahiye.

venv/
env/
.venv/
.env/

2. Database Files

Local database file ko hamesha ignore karein.

instabot_data.db
*.sqlite3

3. Python Cache and Bytecode Files

Yeh files automatically generate hoti hain.

pycache/
*.pyc
*.pyo
*.pyd

4. IDE / Editor Specific Files

Har developer alag editor use kar sakta hai.

.vscode/
.idea/
*.sublime-project
*.sublime-workspace

5. OS Generated Files

Windows, macOS, aur Linux ke system files.

.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

6. Log Files

Agar aap logging use karte hain to inhein ignore karein.

*.log
logs/

7. Credentials & Environment Variables (Most Important)

Password ya secret keys wali files ko kabhi push na karein.

*.env
.env
credentials.py
config.py

8. Flask Specific Files

Flask ka instance folder.

instance/